nodes.text: David Wahlberg is a compositor that has worked in the industry for more than 15 years. He has worked in different visual effects studios around the world in Stockholm, Oslo, London, Sydney, LA and Wellington.[source?] David was nominated for a Visual Effects Society's 2021 award for Outstanding Compositing in an Episode for his work on "Chapter 15: The Believer" of The Mandalorian Notably, David also worked on Star Wars: Episode IX The Rise of Skywalker.
